               <table width="100%" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">
                  <tr>
                     <td width="100%" align="left" class="TableCellHeading">Earthdawn Merchandise Launches!</td>
                  </tr>
                  <tr>
                     <td width="100%" class="TableCellHeading">
                        <p align="right"><i>By James Flowers,
                              June 1, 2004</i></p>
                     </td>
                  </tr>
                  <tr>
                     <td width="100%" align="left" class="TableCell">
                        <p>June 1, 2004 (AUCKLAND, NZ) - RedBrick Limited, publishers of the forthcoming Earthdawn&reg; Classic&#153; game line for FASA Corporation's
                           fantasy roleplaying game in the Age of Legend, are pleased to announce the opening of an online store, which will offer Earthdawn&reg;
                           fans a wide variety of licensed merchandise through partner CafePress.
                        </p>
                        
                        <p>Official licensed Earthdawn-ware is finally here! Beginning June 1st, customers can order a variety of different products
                           - including shirts, hats, coffee mugs, mouse pads and more - incorporating color and line-art imagery from the world of Earthdawn&reg;.
                           Each month more products and images will be added to the store, extending the range of merchandise available.
                        </p>
                        
                        <p>In conjunction with the release of the first books in the Earthdawn&reg; Classic&#153; game line, this online store will provide RedBrick
                           customers and supporters options for prizes or gifts for any special promotions or events we will be involved with.
                        </p>
                        
                        <p>The store is located online at <a href="http://www.cafepress.com/earthdawn">http://www.cafepress.com/earthdawn</a>.
                        </p>
                        
                        <p>The initial product selection features the full color Earthdawn&reg; logo. Additional designs are currently in progress, so please
                           check back regularly to see what else has been added.
                        </p>
                        
                        <p>RedBrick will consider requests for specific items of merchandise, as long as they are selected from those available from
                           the premium CafePress product range. You can visit the Merchandise forum at the Earthdawn&reg; Classic&#153; web site to make your
                           "wish-list" known, or simply to provide feedback.
                        </p>
                        
                        <p>Learn more about RedBrick Limited and visit the Earthdawn&reg; Classic&#153; forums at <a href="http://www.earthdawn-classic.com">http://www.earthdawn-classic.com</a>.
                        </p>
                        
                        <p>Earthdawn&reg; is a Registered Trademark of FASA Corporation. Copyright &copy; 1993 FASA Corporation. Earthdawn&reg; Classic&#153; is a Trademark
                           of FASA Corporation. Copyright &copy; 2004 RedBrick Limited, FASA Corporation. All images and textual content used under license
                           by RedBrick Limited. All Rights Reserved.
                        </p>
                     </td>
                  </tr>
                  <td width="100%" align="right" class="TableCellSmall"><a href="http://www.earthdawn-classic.com/checkShow.html;jsessionid=algl8Alw0Nb_">Back to news items</a></td>
